yah there are varying strategys.  So far I havn't sent in a cleric, necro or paladin to get a DT.  I have cycled just about every other class including chanter (once).<br>
<br>
/agree the deal with fighting DT mobs is to actually have your wizards and druids fight the tanks for aggro...  They need to work their butts off to get on the aggro list.  It is ideal to have the tanks stay alive with some aggro thru the fight... but who is recieveing damage while fighting a DT mob is unimportant... max up front DPS is.  Guy has to drop fast... Idealy within 44 seconds.  If that isn't possible then within 89 seconds.<br>
